1. Mück et al., 2024, *Three-tiered authentication of herbal traditional Chinese medicine ingredients used in women’s health provides progressive qualitative and quantitative insight*：给出原研究问题、公开数据入口及既有图表范式（Venn、分级结果图、abundance grouped results）。([Frontiers][3])
2. Zhou et al., 2025, *DNA metabarcoding unveils authenticity and adulteration in commercial Chinese polyherbal preparations*：提供工作流图、测序指标图、ASV abundance 图、PCoA 图等近年范式，并明确 read abundance 不宜直接回推出原始配方比例。([Frontiers][4])
3. Winand et al., 2025, *assessment of ITS1 and ITS2 Illumina sequencing using multiple defined mock communities*：支持 ITS1/ITS2 互补、不可互换、应晚整合。([Springer][8])
4. Nazar et al., 2024, *Integrating DNA Barcoding Within an Orthogonal Approach for Herbal Product Authentication*：强调 DNA 方法应与其他证据正交互补，支持“主文不夸张到配方定量”。([PMC][10])

### 二、期刊规范 / 方法与报告规范

1. Nature Microbiology, 2025, *Guidelines for preventing and reporting contamination in low-biomass microbiome studies*：强调污染控制、最小报告标准、去污染流程透明化。([Nature][7])
2. Keenum et al., 2023, *Amplicon Sequencing Minimal Information (ASqMI)*：强调 controls checklist、阈值前置、过程记录、AS 更偏定性判断。([OUP Academic][11])
