4. Nature / Scientific Reports submission guidance：图例应自洽、子图用小写粗体字母、线宽和文字需在缩印后可读。([Nature][12])
5. Nature Portfolio reporting standards / reproducibility editorials：审稿前就要求 reporting summary、source data 与透明报告。([Nature][13])

### 三、专栏 / 博客 / 论坛

